==Martuthunira==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/palaʎi/}}
===Etymology===
From Proto-Ngayarda ''*pala'', possibly related to Proto-Pama-Nyungan ''*pala'' "there". See '''[[pala#Martuthunira|pala]]'''.
===Temporal nominal===
'''palalyi'''

# [[before|Before]]; [[earlier]].
